{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ma vie en rogue is a roguelike  spanning multiple themed dungeons and worlds bringing advancements such as a mini-map, first-person view, and paperdoll customization to the genre.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Do you have what it takes to plumb the dungeon's mysteries?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Modern features include:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Themed &quot;worlds&quot;: Adventure in different environments!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1st- and 3rd-person view!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Toggleable mini-map! Keep an eye on your location, or turn it off for extra immersion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Difficulty slider: Adjust your challenge level!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Paperdoll character display! See what you are wearing and wielding.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>With plenty of old-school cool:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hand-drawn pixel art textures, monsters, and items!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Permadeath option: For your traditional rogue-style fate.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn-based action! Play at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Toggleable TV filter effect! Just like your old CRT monitor.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Personalize your character any way you want!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Character creator: Make a player that looks just like you, or try something completely different!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unrestricted color choices for hair and skin. Be green with blue hair, purple with yellow hair; the sky's the limit!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your companion! Which pet will be your favorite?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Name yourself and your pet what you like, or use the random name generator for unique fantasy names!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Challenging and fun!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dozens of monsters to fight, each with its own style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A wide variety of magic items, weapons and armor!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monster taming: Collect new companions!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Friendly NPCs can offer helpful (or unhelpful!) advice and clues.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tricky maze levels!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739342795","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015740/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739342795","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015740/67cec9fadd39024ae879df0ea041299091d2c376/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739342795","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015740/67cec9fadd39024ae879df0ea041299091d2c376/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739342795","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ma vie en rogue is a roguelike  spanning multiple themed dungeons and worlds bringing advancements such as a mini-map, first-person view, and paperdoll customization to the genre.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Do you have what it takes to plumb the dungeon's mysteries?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Modern features include:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Themed &quot;worlds&quot;: Adventure in different environments!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li